{"tid":1325274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"玩香城online前，麻煩做左呢樣先！","createTime":"2019-07-16T23:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T09:15:01.000Z","uid":279159,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ea801ce46757c32ace35b1b2220e89d2e00f90","tid":1325274,"uid":279159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T23:19:51.000Z","msg":"用iOS既記得做以下動作<br />\n<br />\niOSi會無時無刻都在後台追蹤過去所待過的地方，去了多弓，去了多少次。每次停留左幾耐。<br />\n<br />\n清除 iPhone重要位置教學<br />\n<br />\n步驟 1. ▼ 開啟iOS內的「設定」&gt;「隱私權」。<br />\n<br />\n步驟 2. ▼ 點擊「定位服務」。<br />\n<br />\n步驟 3. ▼ 滑到最底點擊「系統服務」。<br />\n<br />\n步驟 4. ▼ 點選「重要位置」。如果是iOS 11以下的功能名稱是「常用位置」<br />\n<br />\n步驟 5. ▼ 這裡就可看見過去所曾經待過的位置記錄，滑到最底會看見「清除歷程記錄」。<br />\n<br />\n步驟 6. ▼ 這跳出確定要重置此iPhone和其它登入 iCloud 帳號裝置上的重要位置嗎？點下「清除歷程記錄」即可。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後，如不希望iOS會一直在記錄這些資訊，那也可以選擇關閉此功能，可到「設定」&gt;「隱私權」&gt;「定位服務」&gt;「系統服務」&gt;「重要位置」內將「重要位置」功能關閉。如果是iOS 11以下的功能名稱是「常用位置」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHKNKFz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHKNKFz.png&h=e872013e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/clear-iphone-significant-locations-data\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fclear-iphone-significant-locations-data&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=075e8463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mrmad.com.tw/clear-iphone-significant-locations-data</a>"},{"pid":"baa15b2ca1d99760e59ac76e8b4ba2ec23540fa1","tid":1325274,"uid":279159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:44:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"895c7d674965749886c8c31c577a4e1fc0f7d21b","tid":1325274,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:11:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6dc2f780ea8bb5000972d2f457cf0c301e919079","tid":1325274,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:11:54.000Z","msg":"唔解鎖"},{"pid":"ed28005551ae220f9ef0be54bcd3838cfa9e1041","tid":1325274,"uid":231922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:20:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Android用家清除位置記錄教學</span></span></strong><br />\n1. 開啟Google Maps內「設定」&gt;「個人內容」<br />\n2. 向下掃直至出現「位置設定」<br />\n3. 點擊「刪除所有「位置記錄」」<br />\n4. 剔選「我明白並要刪除」後點擊「刪除」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如不欲手機繼續記錄將來行蹤，請見以下步驟</span></strong><br />\n5. 返回步驟2並點擊「位置已啟用」<br />\n6. 關閉「使用位置資訊」<br />\n7. 返回步驟2並點擊「位置記錄已開啟」<br />\n8. 關閉「位置記錄」"},{"pid":"7ac227b7e462684944857f3eb47e3b0c87817cce","tid":1325274,"uid":279159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed28005551ae220f9ef0be54bcd3838cfa9e1041","tid":1325274,"uid":231922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:20:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Android用家清除位置記錄教學</span></span></strong><br />\n1. 開啟Google Maps內「設定」&gt;「個人內容」<br />\n2. 向下掃直至出現「位置設定」<br />\n3. 點擊「刪除所有「位置記錄」」<br />\n4. 剔選「我明白並要刪除」後點擊「刪除」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如不欲手機繼續記錄將來行蹤，請見以下步驟</span></strong><br />\n5. 返回步驟2並點擊「位置已啟用」<br />\n6. 關閉「使用位置資訊」<br />\n7. 返回步驟2並點擊「位置記錄已開啟」<br />\n8. 關閉「位置記錄」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"正想搵埋Android👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻"},{"pid":"744291054759ebe14db3545f7cb85ed002bdec04","tid":1325274,"uid":231922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:47:47.000Z","msg":"仲有一招比清除位置記錄更有效<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我唔解鎖！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"fc6a0bf50a6efa7cfa809c4dc953c65977d90266","tid":1325274,"uid":279159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"744291054759ebe14db3545f7cb85ed002bdec04","tid":1325274,"uid":231922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:47:47.000Z","msg":"仲有一招比清除位置記錄更有效<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"